---
// Courses section for Academia Ewaffle
---

<section id="cursos" class="py-20 bg-white relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Background Pattern -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-5">
    <img src="/assets/patronblancobajaopacidad.png" alt="" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
  </div>

  <div class="relative container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">
        Crea contenidos de calidad profesional que cautiven a tu audiencia
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-text-dark max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        A través de clases en vivo y prácticas, dominarás herramientas concretas que puedes aplicar desde el primer día para crear materiales que realmente destaquen:
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Curso 1: Crea la Estructura de tu Curso e-learning -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-20">
      <!-- Text Content -->
      <div>
        <div class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-primary/10 text-primary rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-6">
          <i class="ri-book-open-line mr-2"></i>
          Curso 1
        </div>
        
        <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">
          Crea la Estructura de tu Curso e-learning
        </h3>
        
        <p class="text-lg text-text-dark mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          Aprende a diseñar la estructura completa de tu curso online, desde la propuesta de valor hasta 
          la implementación de recursos multimedia y herramientas de IA.
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-4 mb-8">
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-yellow rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <i class="ri-check-line text-white text-sm"></i>
            </div>
            <span class="text-text-dark">Tu propuesta de valor</span>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-yellow rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <i class="ri-check-line text-white text-sm"></i>
            </div>
            <span class="text-text-dark">Mapa visual del curso</span>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-yellow rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <i class="ri-check-line text-white text-sm"></i>
            </div>
            <span class="text-text-dark">Módulos y recursos sugeridos</span>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-yellow rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <i class="ri-check-line text-white text-sm"></i>
            </div>
            <span class="text-text-dark">Prompts de IA para enriquecer tu enseñanza</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mb-8">
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-2 bg-primary/10 px-4 py-2 rounded-full">
            <i class="ri-time-line text-primary"></i>
            <span class="text-primary font-medium">4 semanas</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-2 bg-accent/10 px-4 py-2 rounded-full">
            <i class="ri-video-line text-accent"></i>
            <span class="text-accent font-medium">Clases en vivo</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-2 bg-yellow/10 px-4 py-2 rounded-full">
            <i class="ri-download-line text-yellow"></i>
            <span class="text-yellow font-medium">Materiales incluidos</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-purple-800 rounded-2xl p-4 text-center">
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-1">$29.000 CLP</div>
            <div class="text-white/80 text-sm">Acceso completo + certificado</div>
          </div>
          
          <a 
            href="#inscripcion"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-secondary text-white rounded-full font-bold text-lg hover:from-primary/90 hover:to-secondary/90 transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transform hover:-translate-y-1"
          >
            <i class="ri-lock-line mr-2"></i>
            Inscribirme ahora
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Course Visual -->
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="relative z-10">
          <div class="w-80 h-80 mx-auto bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-secondary rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-2xl p-8">
            <div class="text-center text-white">
              <i class="ri-book-open-line text-6xl mb-4"></i>
              <div class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Estructura de Curso</div>
              <div class="text-white/80">Diseño instruccional completo</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Floating Elements -->
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-16 h-16 bg-accent/20 rounded-full blur-lg"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-20 h-20 bg-yellow/20 rounded-full blur-lg"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Curso 2: eBooks con Canva -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-20">
      <!-- Text Content -->
      <div>
        <div class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-accent/10 text-accent rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-6">
          <i class="ri-file-text-line mr-2"></i>
          Curso 2
        </div>
        
        <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">
          eBooks con Canva
        </h3>
        
        <p class="text-lg text-text-dark mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          Domina la creación de eBooks profesionales usando Canva. Aprende a diseñar contenido 
          atractivo y funcional que capte la atención de tus estudiantes.
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-4 mb-8">
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-yellow rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <i class="ri-check-line text-white text-sm"></i>
            </div>
            <span class="text-text-dark">Estructura de un ebook profesional</span>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-yellow rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <i class="ri-check-line text-white text-sm"></i>
            </div>
            <span class="text-text-dark">Diseño paso a paso con Canva Doc</span>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-yellow rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <i class="ri-check-line text-white text-sm"></i>
            </div>
            <span class="text-text-dark">Cómo integrar videos y audios</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mb-8">
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-2 bg-primary/10 px-4 py-2 rounded-full">
            <i class="ri-time-line text-primary"></i>
            <span class="text-primary font-medium">3 semanas</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-2 bg-accent/10 px-4 py-2 rounded-full">
            <i class="ri-video-line text-accent"></i>
            <span class="text-accent font-medium">Clases en vivo</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-2 bg-yellow/10 px-4 py-2 rounded-full">
            <i class="ri-download-line text-yellow"></i>
            <span class="text-yellow font-medium">Plantillas incluidas</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-purple-800 rounded-2xl p-4 text-center">
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-1">$25.000 CLP</div>
            <div class="text-white/80 text-sm">Acceso completo + certificado</div>
          </div>
          
          <a 
            href="#inscripcion"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-secondary text-white rounded-full font-bold text-lg hover:from-primary/90 hover:to-secondary/90 transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transform hover:-translate-y-1"
          >
            <i class="ri-lock-line mr-2"></i>
            Inscribirme ahora
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Course Visual -->
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="relative z-10">
          <div class="w-80 h-80 mx-auto bg-gradient-to-br from-accent to-pink-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-2xl p-8">
            <div class="text-center text-white">
              <i class="ri-file-text-line text-6xl mb-4"></i>
              <div class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">eBooks Profesionales</div>
              <div class="text-white/80">Diseño con Canva</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Floating Elements -->
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-16 h-16 bg-accent/20 rounded-full blur-lg"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-20 h-20 bg-yellow/20 rounded-full blur-lg"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Curso 3: Presentaciones Interactivas con H5P -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <!-- Text Content -->
      <div>
        <div class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-yellow/10 text-yellow rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-6">
          <i class="ri-presentation-line mr-2"></i>
          Curso 3
        </div>
        
        <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-primary mb-6">
          Presentaciones Interactivas con H5P
        </h3>
        
        <p class="text-lg text-text-dark mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          Crea experiencias de aprendizaje interactivas y envolventes usando H5P. 
          Aprende a integrar contenido multimedia avanzado en tus cursos.
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-4 mb-8">
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-yellow rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <i class="ri-check-line text-white text-sm"></i>
            </div>
            <span class="text-text-dark">Qué es H5P y cómo usarlo</span>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-yellow rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <i class="ri-check-line text-white text-sm"></i>
            </div>
            <span class="text-text-dark">Cómo crear experiencias interactivas</span>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-yellow rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <i class="ri-check-line text-white text-sm"></i>
            </div>
            <span class="text-text-dark">Cómo integrarlas en tu LMS</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mb-8">
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-2 bg-primary/10 px-4 py-2 rounded-full">
            <i class="ri-time-line text-primary"></i>
            <span class="text-primary font-medium">3 semanas</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-2 bg-accent/10 px-4 py-2 rounded-full">
            <i class="ri-video-line text-accent"></i>
            <span class="text-accent font-medium">Clases en vivo</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-2 bg-yellow/10 px-4 py-2 rounded-full">
            <i class="ri-download-line text-yellow"></i>
            <span class="text-yellow font-medium">Ejemplos prácticos</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-purple-800 rounded-2xl p-4 text-center">
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-1">$25.000 CLP</div>
            <div class="text-white/80 text-sm">Acceso completo + certificado</div>
          </div>
          
          <a 
            href="#inscripcion"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-secondary text-white rounded-full font-bold text-lg hover:from-primary/90 hover:to-secondary/90 transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transform hover:-translate-y-1"
          >
            <i class="ri-lock-line mr-2"></i>
            Inscribirme ahora
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Course Visual -->
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="relative z-10">
          <div class="w-80 h-80 mx-auto bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow to-orange-500 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-2xl p-8">
            <div class="text-center text-white">
              <i class="ri-presentation-line text-6xl mb-4"></i>
              <div class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Contenido Interactivo</div>
              <div class="text-white/80">H5P y multimedia</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Floating Elements -->
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-16 h-16 bg-accent/20 rounded-full blur-lg"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-20 h-20 bg-yellow/20 rounded-full blur-lg"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section> 